<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>The Carpet Cleaning Company | Website Design for Carpet Cleaners</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Beautiful website design and technical build services for carpet cleaners. Landing pages, SEO focused sites, quote funnels, review pages, and specialist digital support from The Carpet Cleaning Company." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f7fbff;
      --bg-soft: #ffffff;
      --panel: rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      --panel-strong: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      --text: #0b1b2b;
      --muted: #5f7287;
      --line: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --accent: #4fc3f7;
      --accent-2: #1e88e5;
      --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --radius: 24px;
      --radius-sm: 18px;
      --max: 1240px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79,195,247,0.12), transparent 40%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f7fbff 0%, #eef6fc 100%);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(143,211,255,0.25), rgba(255,255,255,0.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .brand-copy {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-copy strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand-copy span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .nav-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ffffff);
      color: #07111f;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(143,211,255,0.18);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 72px 0 36px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 78px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .hero h1 .glow {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(143,211,255,0.12);
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(16px, 2.1vw, 20px);
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 15px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ffffff);
      color: #07111f;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(143,211,255,0.2);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .trust-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .trust-pill {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .screen {
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      background: #07111f;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    .screen-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: #0d1b2d;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
    }

    .screen-body {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 520px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), rgba(255,255,255,0.6)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520607162513-77705c0f0d4a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      padding: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .floating-site {
      max-width: 360px;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(7,17,31,0.84);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .floating-site small {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .floating-site h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .floating-site p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 36px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .cards-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .cards-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .card .icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(143,211,255,0.2), rgba(255,255,255,0.06));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .feature-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .feature-item b {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .process-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .step-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 54px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      color: #07111f;
    }

    .step h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .step p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .showcase {
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 100%;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.02)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      position: relative;
    }

    .showcase::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(7,17,31,0.16), rgba(7,17,31,0.74));
    }

    .showcase-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: end;
      gap: 14px;
      min-height: 100%;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .showcase-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .showcase h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.03;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      max-width: 460px;
    }

    .showcase p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 500px;
      color: #dbe8f5;
    }

    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .price-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 26px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .price-card.featured {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(79,195,247,0.15), #ffffff);
      border-color: rgba(79,195,247,0.4);
      transform: translateY(-6px);
    }

    .price-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .price-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .price {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .price span {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .price-card p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .price-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .price-list li {
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 18px;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .price-list li::before {
      content: "•";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .final-cta {
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .final-cta h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }

    .final-cta p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 650px;
    }

    .contact-panel {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
      background: #f7fbff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .contact-panel h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .contact-panel p {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .contact-links {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding: 28px 0 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .site-footer .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .process-wrap,
      .final-cta,
      .cards-3,
      .pricing-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .cards-2 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .price-card.featured { transform: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding-top: 42px; }
      .hero h1 { line-height: 1; }
      .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn { width: 100%; }
      .screen-body { min-height: 420px; padding: 18px; }
      .floating-site { max-width: 100%; }
      .section-head { display: block; }
      .section-head p { margin-top: 10px; }
      .card, .price-card, .final-cta, .hero-card { padding: 20px; }
      .showcase-content { padding: 20px; }
      .showcase h3 { font-size: 28px; }
      .contact-link { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#top" class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark">TC</div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <strong>The Carpet Cleaning Company</strong>
          <span>Website design for carpet cleaners</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
        <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get your site built</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Beautiful websites for carpet cleaners</div>
          <h1>Websites that make <span class="glow">carpet cleaners</span> look premium, trustworthy, and worth booking.</h1>
          <p>I build beautiful, high converting website pages for carpet cleaners, along with technical digital help that makes the business feel sharper, more modern, and easier to grow online.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start your website project</a>
            <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">See what I can build</a>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-row">
            <div class="trust-pill">Landing pages that look premium</div>
            <div class="trust-pill">Built for carpet cleaning businesses</div>
            <div class="trust-pill">SEO focused structure</div>
            <div class="trust-pill">Technical help beyond the website</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="screen">
            <div class="screen-bar">
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="screen-body">
              <div class="floating-site">
                <small>Luxury lead generation</small>
                <h2>Designed to turn cleaners into brands</h2>
                <p>Premium visuals, stronger wording, better trust signals, clearer service pages, and a site that feels far above the average local cleaner.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>What I can build for carpet cleaners</h2>
          </div>
          <p>This is not just a basic brochure site. It is website design and practical digital development aimed at helping carpet cleaners look established, modern, and easier to choose.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-3">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">✦</div>
            <h3>Beautiful landing pages</h3>
            <p>High end home pages and campaign pages built to look premium, feel trustworthy, and make the business stand out against weak local competitors.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">⌘</div>
            <h3>Service and area pages</h3>
            <p>Pages for carpet cleaning, upholstery cleaning, stain removal, commercial work, and local town coverage designed to help with visibility and conversions.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">⚙</div>
            <h3>Technical development help</h3>
            <p>Help with quote pages, review funnels, lead forms, call to action flows, lightweight systems, and useful tools that support the business beyond the main website.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container process-wrap">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:18px; display:block;">
            <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);">Built around what actually wins bookings</h2>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">Most cleaner websites look dated, generic, or cheap. The aim here is to create pages that feel stronger, cleaner, and far more premium.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-list">
            <div class="feature-item"><span>01</span><div><b>Premium visual direction</b><br>Sharper layouts, stronger spacing, cleaner typography, and a more expensive overall feel.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-item"><span>02</span><div><b>Wording that sells value</b><br>Less weak generic filler, more trust, proof, positioning, and proper service language.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-item"><span>03</span><div><b>Made for local service businesses</b><br>Built around phone calls, quote requests, service pages, area pages, and trust building.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-item"><span>04</span><div><b>Ongoing digital help</b><br>Useful support for pages, tools, lead magnets, and technical ideas that can help the business grow.</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="card showcase">
          <div class="showcase-content">
            <div class="showcase-badge">Positioning</div>
            <h3>Not a cheap looking cleaner site. A cleaner brand.</h3>
            <p>The goal is to make a carpet cleaning company look more premium, more capable, and more established from the first few seconds on the page.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="process">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>How the build process works</h2>
          </div>
          <p>A simple process focused on getting a beautiful result without the site turning into a bloated mess.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-list">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Style direction</h3>
              <p>We decide the feel of the site. Premium, modern, local, luxury, commercial, or more aggressive lead focused depending on what suits the business.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Page structure</h3>
              <p>The page gets built around what carpet cleaners actually need such as service sections, trust signals, review areas, quote forms, and location targeting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Technical extras</h3>
              <p>If needed, the build can go further with supporting pages, digital tools, review funnels, or custom lead handling ideas that improve how the business operates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Refinement</h3>
              <p>Then the site is polished so it looks clean on desktop and mobile, feels more expensive, and is ready to present properly to customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="packages">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
